{"type":"message","id":"95918ee0","parentId":"04120b18","timestamp":"2026-04-03T03:25:20.313Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ahora dejo todo registrado en memoria."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01VFzqU9WkUaqmmcNXCTZQxr","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"$d=Get-Date -Format 'yyyy-MM-dd'; $p='C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\'+$d+'.md'; Add-Content -Path $p -Value \"`n- Reordenamiento completo de automatismos: reviews de Atlas OS (morning/midday/end-of-day) desactivados; Ares/Hestia/Prometeo ahora tienen heartbeats propios con contexto de Notion por dominio y voz propia; Atlas pulse reducido a solo bloqueos transversales reales (máximo 2 líneas, sin informe); email reviews acortados a max 240s y máximo 3 líneas sin formato. Regla activa: Atlas no ventriloquea, no redacta como los agentes, no genera informe de tablero automático.\"","workdir":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\workspace","yieldMs":8000,"timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":329,"cacheRead":67735,"cacheWrite":2907,"totalTokens":70972,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775186709172,"responseId":"msg_01MHFJzeRXzor5qTge457eVf"}}
